div.p:
FOr to retayne the marchaundyſe of Horſes in our countrees to the welthe & profyte of many of our ſubgectes that make marchaundyſe of them / we haue defended and forfo
                     ••
                  ) to all perſones be they oure ſubgectes or ſtraungers to carye any Mares out of our ſayde countrees / On payne of forfeytoure of the ſayde Mares / and alſo the valoure of them the halfe to our vſe One quarter to the fynder / and the other quarter to the offycer that executeth it.
